      {
         "id": "SECTION_introduction",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>We need couting</h3>In our lives, we always have something to count: our age, our friends, or our toys. Observe <b>Figure 1</b>, which shows indigenous musical instruments from Costa Rica:</p><p class=\"desc\"> <img id=\"img0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img0', '0%')\" src=\"images/SanJoseCRMuseo/MusicCR.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\" /><b>Figure 1</b>: Musical instruments present in Costa Rica (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('3e4dc8f8-8c2b-491e-9e2b-0b3adb927c70'); return false;\">Museo Nacional de Costa Rica</a>). Photo taken during a visit to the museum on <htdate0></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2017",
                     "month": "10",
                     "day": "17"
                  }
               ],
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "In this image, we observe woodwind instruments with a mouthpiece at the top and a perforated shell at the bottom.",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 1: Couting with our body</b><br />On the previous page, we began to learn about our body. Now, think: is there a part of our body that we can use to count?</div></div></center></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_hands",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Counting with our hands</h3>We can address our problem by using each finger to count a unique object:</p><p><table class=\"book_navigation\"><tr><td>Left hand</td><td>Right hand</td></tr><tr><td><img id=\"img1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img1', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/Hand_Grape.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td><td><img id=\"img2\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img2', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/RHand_Grape.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Figure 2</b>: Representation of our hands. Source code available on the project's GitHub (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('240800f3-ede4-4deb-9d4e-915a3a03fa68'); return false;\">History Tracers Team, <htdate0>, Source code</a>)</td></tr></table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  }
               ],
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "The figure shows a person's two hands raised with all fingers extended, each pointing toward a fruit.",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_testing",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>One by one</h3><b>Figure 1</b> as fewer musical instruments than we typically have fingers on our hands. How can we count a few objects? The first step is to become familiar with our fingers:</p><p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"img3\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img3', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/Hand_Finger.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 3</b>: Fingers of a left hand: <b>A</b> - Thumb, <b>B</b> - Index, <b>C</b> - Middle, <b>D</b> - Ring, <b>E</b> - Little. The source code is available in GitHub of the project (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('240800f3-ede4-4deb-9d4e-915a3a03fa68'); return false;\">History Tracers Team, <htdate0>, CÃ³digo-fonte</a>).</p>Now that we know our fingers, we will raise one finger at a time to do the counting:</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  }
               ],
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<table class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th>Left hand</th><th>Description</th><th>Right hand</th></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img4\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img4', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers down.</td><td><img id=\"img5\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img5', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img6\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img6', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Right index finger raised.</td><td><img id=\"img7\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img7', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/1Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img8\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img8', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Index and middle fingers of the right hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img9\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img9', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/2Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img10\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img10', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Index, middle and ring of the right hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img11\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img11', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/3Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img12\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img12', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Index, middle, ring and little of the right hand raised</td><td><img id=\"img13\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img13', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/4Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img14\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img14', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/0Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers of the right hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img15\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img15', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img16\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img16', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/1Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers of the right hand raised, and index of the left hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img17\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img17', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img18\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img18', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/2Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers of the right hand raised, with index and middle of the left hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img19\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img19', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img20\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img20', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/3Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers of the right hand raised, with index, middle and ring of the left hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img21\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img21', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img22\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img22', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/4Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\" style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers of the right hand raised, with index, middle, ring and little of the left hand raised.</td><td><img id=\"img23\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img23', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> <tr><td><img id=\"img24\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img24', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Left_Hand_Small.png\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">All fingers raised.</td><td><img id=\"img25\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img25', '0%')\" src=\"images/HistoryTracers/5Right_Hand_Small.png\" /></td></tr> </table>",
